{"tid":2354883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣都係情緒後反應慢半拍既人","createTime":"2021-01-05T23:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T05:52:21.000Z","uid":207890,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11f4f2d6d1c772725c684214911cdd6baa8b9a84","tid":2354883,"uid":207890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:03:56.000Z","msg":"話說 呢排失戀 工作 同 家人既問題接種而來<br />\n我最親既呀婆呢排又過咗身..<br />\n但我好似無反應 無感受咁<br />\n一滴眼淚都無喊流過<br />\n已經唔清楚係我本身無感受定點...然於我好冷靜咁諗<br />\n由細到大都係啲後知後覺既人<br />\n姐係發生個一下其實無咩感受<br />\n但唔知點解事後諗返 可能一星期無啦啦諗諗下會喊會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似當下唔係好識得表達自己既感受<br />\n例如同人嘈交咁 發生個下唔會好嬲<br />\n但事後會愈諗愈嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d2a025dd74e0bb60767653cda8d230321c8d15","tid":2354883,"uid":207890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:05:09.000Z","msg":"有冇師兄都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有冇人讀psycho解答下me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d3ef0883375f2e33e17b5cc1e8d89f108ef992","tid":2354883,"uid":207890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"其實我意識到自己「應該」要喊<br />\n要傷心 但我真係喊唔出<br />\n係咪麻木咗"},{"pid":"b24dd5e8b69d18abb3651d19603ee2654949c046","tid":2354883,"uid":223977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:12:17.000Z","msg":"原來唔係得我係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一直都有依個感覺，例如對上一次失戀，分手個刻咩事都無，無任何感覺，照常咁生活。<br />\n<br />\n但過左兩個月左右開始先識得傷心咁，係突然間好似後知後覺咁，會調返轉成日諗起件事，每次諗起都唔開心，仲無胃口左食個星期。"},{"pid":"b2c2b520ad4f2e9d31b958fd05e5a5f8bed8c5fd","tid":2354883,"uid":218219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:19:49.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954d0dd4630d0837a84650dd01fc1928fa818f8e","tid":2354883,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fd186cc9bf8005ddd263b13368b14215d3e6c5","tid":2354883,"uid":207890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"954d0dd4630d0837a84650dd01fc1928fa818f8e","tid":2354883,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"真明明覺得好關心<br />\n但表現到好似無野咁"},{"pid":"e702fc167906f94a2c5e90e371c3fecf059913f2","tid":2354883,"uid":207890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b24dd5e8b69d18abb3651d19603ee2654949c046","tid":2354883,"uid":223977,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:12:17.000Z","msg":"原來唔係得我係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一直都有依個感覺，例如對上一次失戀，分手個刻咩事都無，無任何感覺，照常咁生活。<br />\n<br />\n但過左兩個月左右開始先識得傷心咁，係突然間好似後知後覺咁，會調返轉成日諗起件事，每次諗起都唔開心，仲無胃口左食個星期。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"啱先無原因咁被分手⋯⋯<br />\n我無感覺⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c4bde3f0967187a933d43abff950af89d87e9617","tid":2354883,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"有病就睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"351e522ba60be0dabb2dfe1008a9619f1bb606e4","tid":2354883,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"我，過咗幾分鐘至幾日後先識嬲同驚同喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n面對危險時幾方便"}]}